Active Land is a sports-related new-tab extension, allowing users to easily access and explore a wide range of this field by quick and simple search features.

By clicking "add to Chrome", I accept and agree to installing the Active Land extension and setting Chrome New Tab to that provider by the service and the Terms of Use (https://activeland.co/terms-of-conditions/) and Policy (https://activeland.co/privacy-policy/). The extension will update your search settings and will change your new tab and default search provider to Microsoft Bing.

For more information please visit https://activeland.co/
